title: Knife
description: Lower edge of blade straight, the upper edge tapering towards the point. Tapered handles with flat sides, open scrolls at the top. Engraved figural designs: on one side "TOBIEAS" and "AQUA", on the other side "IONES" and "TERRA".  Engraved on handle: "Maria Brainne 1621."
